  "detailed_description": "Panzer Battalion is a top-down shooter that, unlike the current tank battle mode, is a bit more arcade-oriented.<br>Simulations of real physics were carried out, such as artillery recoil.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are also bumps in the march of the tank, shooting inaccuracy .<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The campaign mode can familiarize players with the game, and the RPG mode of the open map is made later.<br>Divided into two camps, tanks can be assembled at will.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The open map has an area of more than 300 square kilometers and has a main campaign planned from Barbarossa to Berlin that is unlocked sequentially.<br>There are random chests and camps in the wild, and more elements will be added later.",
  "about_the_game": "Panzer Battalion is a top-down shooter that, unlike the current tank battle mode, is a bit more arcade-oriented.<br>Simulations of real physics were carried out, such as artillery recoil.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/e6593834a86b213aa510ab2196507b7e.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are also bumps in the march of the tank, shooting inaccuracy .<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/45b43dc26859795bedda9b88c3ec4281.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The campaign mode can familiarize players with the game, and the RPG mode of the open map is made later.<br>Divided into two camps, tanks can be assembled at will.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.poster.avif?t=1683011948\" width=480 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.webm?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027600/extras/0efb6a208d8611c89da2ea03673b8915.mp4?t=1683011948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The open map has an area of more than 300 square kilometers and has a main campaign planned from Barbarossa to Berlin that is unlocked sequentially.<br>There are random chests and camps in the wild, and more elements will be added later.",
